## üìñ ABAP Keyword Explanations
| Keyword       | Purpose |
|---------------|---------|
| `TABLES`      | Links dictionary table to program. |
| `PARAMETERS`  | Single input field on selection screen. |
| `SELECT-OPTIONS` | Multiple/range input on selection screen. |
| `DATA`        | Declares variables, internal tables, work areas. |
| `SELECT ... INTO TABLE` | Retrieves DB data into an internal table. |
| `WHERE ... OR ...` | Conditional filter in the query. |
| `SY-SUBRC`    | System return code after statements. |
| `MESSAGE`     | Displays a message to the user. |
| `LOOP AT`     | Iterates through an internal table. |
| `WRITE`       | Outputs data to the list screen. |

